            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deabus Aufani<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied> <lb n="2"/>pro salute Invicti <lb n="3"/>Antonini <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Aurelius Agripinus <lb n="5"/>b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ädikula mit der Darstellung dreier sitzender Matronen.</p>
            </div>
